{"tid":982831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分歧仍大！WSJ：中美代表北京談判連初步協議都無","createTime":"2019-01-15T12:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T15:21:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9af03535dcabc9e90609c08079df3264a0cfff33","tid":982831,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547546754_6821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190115%2Flarge%2F1547546754_6821.jpg&h=74fbf050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美代表上星期在北京舉行副部級談判，將原來的兩日會期延長至三日，外界認為談判有大進展，習近平經濟智囊、國務院副總理劉鶴更可能訪美，進一步商談並達成協議，結束貿易戰。不過，美國《華爾街日報》引述消息人士透露，這次副部級談判，中美雙方其實只是「各自澄清立場」，「連初步協議都無」，更稱雙方分歧仍大，離達成共識還有一大段距離。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指出，上星期在北京的談判中，中方雖然同意有必要履行雙方可能達成的協議，但卻沒有承諾採取甚麼具體方法執行，這顯示中美雙方分歧仍大。<br />\n<br />\n美國財長姆欽早前估計，副總理劉鶴將於月底訪問美國華盛頓，與美國貿易代表萊特希澤（Robert Lighthizer）等官員繼續進行貿易談判，但未有定出劉鶴訪問的具體日期。分析認為，這場高級別談判相當重要，有望促成雙方作出關鍵決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190115/59146266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F59146266&d=YyosyXkv3krQ3%2BbqA6FPNC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=73493059\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F59146266&h=0fbc53ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190115/59146266</a>"},{"pid":"5c667499a47a1ff51775f2342fb771ef7dfa9e90","tid":982831,"uid":171866,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"開支那波啦<br />\n拉長時間美國自己唔捱得幾耐"},{"pid":"60a1a482dd159a5000a20b89c35e40f71e2a2b91","tid":982831,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"牛逼死了"},{"pid":"b9b643a11df0064d616ae740c0b23732eecc583c","tid":982831,"uid":41545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"其實係咪比90日時間美商走得就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從頭到尾都係搞撚掂支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e72ba05eca3d5eff9b8f86b5349b0f0d8c2769c","tid":982831,"uid":95497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c667499a47a1ff51775f2342fb771ef7dfa9e90","tid":982831,"uid":171866,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"開支那波啦<br />\n拉長時間美國自己唔捱得幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"3月1日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c5a51c22854fc4c0801f39d5591ae86507e01e","tid":982831,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"慢慢傾<br />\n傾到侵侵任期完都未傾完"},{"pid":"e2ec96b2c0c5388758758df43bfb780d8e7e8a46","tid":982831,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔緊要<br />\n港獨聯關愛座hunter會支持中國貨品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}